<L>__{interior central communications berlin night}
<A>__{once again the operators are frozen, looking at lt. haans. he in turn looks at two orders in his hands. he is deeply confused. sgt. helm is not.}
<C>__{helm}
<D>__{it's a coup all right... and when it's over, we'd better wind up on the right side. now we can't afford to remain neutral any longer. we have to make a decision.}
<A>__{close on: haans. all eyes watch him weigh the decision of his life, of many lives. millions in fact. finally he relents, handing one paper to helm.}
